643
00:39:56,945 --> 00:39:59,485
I was trying to fix
what the waves washed up

644
00:39:59,575 --> 00:40:02,125
so I went out on the boat by myself.

645
00:40:02,315 --> 00:40:05,805
That's when I saw something holding
onto the buoy out in the water.

646
00:40:05,895 --> 00:40:11,595
I wanted to see what it was,
so I went out there with all my might.

647
00:40:11,735 --> 00:40:13,745
Oh, my goodness.

648
00:40:14,465 --> 00:40:16,705
And you know what that was?

649
00:40:17,015 --> 00:40:20,195
-None other than your brother!
-Seriously, Father.

650
00:40:20,385 --> 00:40:23,025
