That's what happened.

671
00:41:17,575 --> 00:41:21,655
-Because he's caught in bad waters...
-Father!

672
00:41:21,805 --> 00:41:23,745
Father! Father!

673
00:41:24,135 --> 00:41:25,235
Stop calling him 'Father'.

674
00:41:25,325 --> 00:41:27,579
Who are you? Who are you to come here?

675
00:41:29,115 --> 00:41:30,285
What was that sound?

676
00:41:31,425 --> 00:41:32,675
Father!

677
00:41:33,865 --> 00:41:35,480
-Father!
-Grandfather!

678
00:41:36,234 --> 00:41:37,761
Get me a pillow and a blanket.

679
00:41:38,123 --> 00:41:39,505
Hurry!

680
00:41:41,665 --> 00:41:43,465
Father doesn't have dementia.

681
00:41:43,555 --> 00:41:45,248
